originalText.text: I’ve been trying to get ahold of this company for weeks about an issue I have with shipping. They responded at first (someone named Mike) and he wouldn’t answer my questions at all. I paid for 2 day shipping and they took over a month to even ship the shirts I bought ($12.75 shipping price) and when I asked them for a refund on this price they told me that it’s not unusual for shipping regardless of the rate to take over 15 business days to ship out. I asked for them to direct me to this disclaimer and they closed the chat. I asked them for this disclaimer again and they repeated themselves over and over without answering where the disclaim could be found on their site. I’ve now emailed them 5 times asking for help (over the course of weeks) and they’ve yet to respond since. Will not buy from here anymore I’d rather get stuff from a company that pretends to care about their customers

originalText.text: Been waiting over two months for my order. Last heard from them at the start of October when they said they were awaiting shipment to their UK warehouse - this was a month AFTER I'd placed my order (with the website not saying it was out of stock or to expect a long wait)! The kicker is, they still list the item I ordered for sale on the website without, again, saying it's out of stock in the UK warehouse or to expect an extended delivery. Company has made no attempt to contact me, to keep me updated about the status of my order, or even so much as to apologise for what is a completely unacceptable wait time. Safe to say, I'll be avoiding this company in the future and will refuse to buy any merch that is created and dispatched by them.

I was wanting to wear this t-shirt for a concert in 4 days. It took me to inquire before they even looked!

originalText.text: Pre-ordered Weezer's new album Pacific Daydream from them, the package was supposed to arrive on October 27th when the album came out, as of this writing it is November 5th and I still have not received it. They sent out a digital download code and a lame "problem at the plant" excuse and basically told us you will get your products when we feel like getting around to it. Wish I could do 0 stars.
